grievance.template:
Subject: Grievance regarding undue delay in processing {application_type} (Ref: {application_number})

Respected Sir/Madam,

I submitted an application for {application_type} on {application_date} at {office_name}. The application has been pending for {days_pending} days, which exceeds the expected timeline as per Citizen Charter.

I request urgent intervention to:
1) Provide the current status and reasons for delay.
2) Ensure time-bound disposal of the application.
3) Share the escalation officer details for follow-up.

Details:
- Applicant: {applicant_name}
- Contact: {phone}, {email}
- Office: {office_address}

Thank you.
{applicant_name}
